item.title: By: JenW
item.dc:creator: JenW
item.description: Oh my gosh - I am going through the same thing! I know how bad for me it is. I usually spend my summers pretty pale and for some reason, this summer, I have been itching to get out in the sun. I blame my new cute swimsuit. It's been about 5 years since I bought myself a swimsuit.
item.content:encoded: Oh my gosh – I am going through the same thing! I know how bad for me it is. I usually spend my summers pretty pale and for some reason, this summer, I have been itching to get out in the sun. I blame my new cute swimsuit. It’s been about 5 years since I bought myself a swimsuit.
